author: Written by: FOX8Live.com Staff
title: Man arrives at hospital with gunshot wound to chest
text:
NEW ORLEANS, LA (WVUE) - Police are investigating a shooting that wounded a 25-year-old man Thursday in New Orleans East.
The incident happened at about 7 p.m. in the 4600 block of Longfellow Drive.
Police said the man showed up at a hospital with a gunshot wound to the chest.
Fox8live.com will update this story as information is released.
